# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NON-NEGOTIABLE
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# - PROJECT.md and phase specs are the source of truth. Always.
# - Pydantic models for ALL data. No raw dicts crossing module boundaries.
# - LLM outputs configs. Templates write code. Never the other way around.
# - All amounts use Decimal. All dates use timezone-aware datetime.
# - Every generated adapter is deterministic — same config = same code every time.
# - Human-in-the-loop for all mapping approvals. No auto-deploying adapters.
# - Insurance domain terminology must be correct. "Excess" is not "premium."
# - Every phase ends with passing tests before moving to the next phase.
# - Commit after every working feature. No mega-commits.
# - Zero tolerance for: bare Exception catches, print() debugging, Any types,
#   hardcoded secrets, float for money, naive datetimes.
